---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Authorized Distributors — Rentar Fuel Catalyst | Rentar"
  description="Rentar Fuel Catalyst products are available only through Rentar or officially authorized distributors. Verify your supplier before purchasing."
>
  <section class="hero" style="min-height:40vh;">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-tag">Distribution</p>
      <h1 style="font-size:2.6rem;">Authorized Distributors</h1>
      <p>Every genuine Rentar Fuel Catalyst originates through Rentar or an authorized distribution partner operating under Rentar's written approval and ongoing commercial supervision.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="manifesto-block">
        <p>To protect customers, product integrity, and technical support, Rentar products are available only through Rentar or officially authorized distributors. Authorized distributors operate under Rentar's written authorization, commercial supervision, product training, quality standards, branding requirements, and technical support program.</p>

        <p class="highlight-label" style="font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);font-size:1.15rem;margin-top:32px;">Verify Your Supplier</p>
        <p>If you are considering the purchase of a Rentar Fuel Catalyst, we encourage you to verify that your supplier is currently authorized by Rentar. Purchasing through an authorized distributor ensures:</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none; padding-left:0; margin-bottom:24px;">
          <li style="padding:6px 0; color:var(--gray-text);">Genuine Rentar products</li>
          <li style="padding:6px 0; color:var(--gray-text);">Factory backed technical support</li>
          <li style="padding:6px 0; color:var(--gray-text);">Current product specifications</li>
          <li style="padding:6px 0; color:var(--gray-text);">Warranty eligibility</li>
          <li style="padding:6px 0; color:var(--gray-text);">Access to engineering assistance</li>
          <li style="padding:6px 0; color:var(--gray-text);">Ongoing customer support</li>
        </ul>

        <div style="background:var(--white); border:1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius:8px; padding:32px; margin:32px 0; box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);">
          <h3 style="font-size:1.3rem; font-weight:600; color:var(--navy); margin-bottom:12px;">Verify a Reseller</h3>
          <p style="font-size:1rem; color:var(--gray-text); margin-bottom:16px;">Before purchasing, confirm your supplier is currently authorized by Rentar.</p>
          <a href="/downloads/Rentar_Verification_Advisory_Professional.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary" style="display:inline-block;">Verify Reseller</a>
          <p style="margin-top:20px; font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--gray-mid);">Questions? <a href="mailto:info@rentar.com" style="color:var(--orange);">info@rentar.com</a></p>
        </div>

        <p class="highlight-label" style="font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);font-size:1.15rem;margin-top:32px;">Become an Authorized Distributor</p>
        <p>Rentar selectively partners with qualified organizations serving industrial markets worldwide. Authorized partners receive technical training, sales support, marketing resources, territory development, engineering assistance, and factory support. Interested in becoming an authorized distributor? Contact our commercial team.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:center; margin-top:48px;">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Sales</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
